  <brief_title>S90652 in Paediatric Hypertension</brief_title>
  <official_title>Acceptability, Safety, Pharmacokinetics and Effects on Blood Pressure of a Daily Dose of 0.025 to 0.135 Milligram Per Kilogram of S90652, a Paediatric Formulation of Perindopril, in 2-16 Years Old Hypertensive Children - 3 Month Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
